name: 10 Seat Table at IRCO Asian Family Center presents Asian Pacific Cultural Night Ticket
description:
A Full table of 10 for you and your community to enjoy!

When: May 10th, 2013 7-10pm
Where: The Governor Hotel, 614 SW 11th Ave, Portland, OR 97205

We are very proud to be celebrating our almost two decades of outstanding service to the Asian and Pacific Islander communities of Portland. This event will be celebrating the past several years and raising funds to continue IRCO AFC’s services into the future. Tickets are $100.00 and every dollar you donate will go directly to IRCO AFC programming. The evening will be full of world music, food, dance and celebration with Portland’s business and community leaders. We look forward to see you there!”
